contentstackProductList.title: Acer Laptop
contentstackProductList.subline: ACER ASPIRE E1-571G CORE I5 BRIEF DESCRIPTION
contentstackProductList.description:
The Acer Aspire E1-571G Core i5 laptop is powered by Intel Core i5 (3rd generation) 2.6 GHz With Turbo Boost up to 3.2 GHz dual core processor and run on Linux OS. It has NVIDIA GeForce GT 710M graphics processor with 2GB DDR3 dedicated graphics memory.

Acer  Aspire E1-571G Core i5 has 4 GB DDR3 RAM, 500 GB HDD and an integrated DVD Drive. It has a 15.6 inch HD TFT LCD Display with LED Backlit with 1366 x 768 pixels resolution.
